## Final report

**File edited:** `proofs/lean/extraction/Clever_041_incr_listObligations.lean`

**All four obligations closed:**

1. **`incr_list_total`** ŌĆö proven via `incr_list_aux` (which discharges the success-case strong induction `incr_at_correct`).
2. **`incr_list_length`** ŌĆö case-split on whether any element overflows; the overflow case contradicts `hres = RustM.ok v` via `incr_list_fail_aux`, the no-overflow case reduces to `incr_list_aux`'s length conjunct.
3. **`incr_list_elementwise`** ŌĆö same case-split structure; the no-overflow case extracts the elementwise conjunct from `incr_list_aux`.
4. **`incr_list_overflow_fails`** ŌĆö direct application of `incr_list_fail_aux`.

**Proof scaffolding added** (mirrors `clever_021_rescale_to_unit_modified`'s `shift_at` pattern):

